  <aspecttable>basic-enhanced</aspecttable>
  <name>Triple searchlight high signal</name>
  <reference>(similar to basic signals described in various magazine articles)</reference>
  <description>A three-headed signal inspired by masts used in the "basic" signal system.
    This mast adds a third head and an Advanced Approach appearance.  This mast can be used
    where two divergent paths exist (e.g. two turnouts) that are too close to be signaled
    by separate masts.
  </description>

